        <td bgColor="black"><textarea cols="70" name="Message" rows="12" wrap="VIRTUAL">[quote]
Ok.. i've been in a few groups where the add's got bad enough for one chanter to not be able to breathe in wich i helped the mezin'n and kept the chanter alive with shadowbond (only when everything was mezed did i heal). So i was grouping in seb for kicks last nite and we had a chanter, he was doing a horrible job at mez'in and i was saving him left and right with ST. He would bitch at me to stop mez'in and telling me to stop shadowbonding him even though if it werent for me he would be dead (not the group mind you i was doing a better mez job than him). After he left (thank god) we got another enchanter and i went through the same shit getting yelled at for mez'in with ST and healing the chanter while i was keeping the chanter alive and doing a fair job at mez'in... anyone care to explain to me why these chanters are such morons?

[url="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=221490"]Malarix[/url] - Dark Elf Heretic of E'ci - Level 54

